    At the 2025 Quantum Techniques in Machine Learning conference, research on kernel-based dequantization of quantum machine learning examined classical kernel-based methods as dequantization methods for quantum models based on parameterized quantum circuits, including quantum neural networks and quantum kernel methods.
    
