    ## Key Research Areas
    
    **Recent Work on p-adic L-functions (2025-2026):**
    
    Recently published work in Compositio Mathematica (November 2025) presents p-adic interpolation of Gauss–Manin connections on nearly overconvergent modular forms. This research has immediate applications to the construction of p-adic L-functions for the triple product of modular forms and for the Rankin-Selberg product of two modular forms, allowing construction of three-variable versions of these p-adic L-functions without certain restrictions on the weight.
    
